{"tid":1692921,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"徐天佑最憎又黃又藍","createTime":"2019-11-04T10:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T10:03:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0b79506e117ae87ee9d3ac9582b7d4a30b6cde02","tid":1692921,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:13:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191104/20799431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191104%2F20799431&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWflpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=17b4b1c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191104%2F20799431&h=5d8b386e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191104/20799431</a><br />\n<br />\n徐天佑最憎又黃又藍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191104/large/1572787307_aa15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191104%2Flarge%2F1572787307_aa15.jpg&h=e0735949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n徐天佑沒指名道姓，但黃又南成為嫌疑人物。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n徐天佑一向就反送中活動敢於發言，盛傳跟Shine拍檔黃又南意見不合而分道揚鑣。前日是黃又南生日，他在fb撰文回憶18年前入行時很多的「第一次」，表示不知道幾時還會有機會唱《18相送》，暗示Shine要分開一段時間，還叫大家不用擔心他。當時有人留言「五大訴求，缺一不可」，一向沒談政治立場的又南以「加油」回覆。<br />\n<br />\n天佑未知是否因此觸動神經，同日也在fb留言：「最憎人，假到呢，不過算，唔想畀負能量出嚟，做好自己。」雖然沒指名道姓，但有心水清網民留言：「又黃又藍，扮晒兩邊。」與又南名字諧音相近，天佑忍不住畀like。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：葉晴 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n睇好票房勁過《棟篤》 宗師黃子華 搶賀歲一哥<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n鍾達茵餐廳結業蝕逾五百萬"},{"pid":"c40ce0b7fe6cde85bffd8770537cd7139102c3a2","tid":1692921,"uid":163055,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:14:12.000Z","msg":"天佑bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec2e9db164ffd5a6d8adf0e2e92dedfe9094f54","tid":1692921,"uid":109820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:14:12.000Z","msg":"推順便借位<br />\n<br />\n【認真參考日本社運】想行得遠過藍絲，不如唔好再鬧同路人啲ig？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692734</a>"},{"pid":"b18ed32a672317018240a818e803a9e5dbe0ce45","tid":1692921,"uid":132587,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:14:43.000Z","msg":"呢五個月真係睇清楚好多人既真面目<br />\n遠至藝人<br />\n近至屋企人同朋友<br />\n原本性格好好既去撐警 完全失望"},{"pid":"3b8d3aff0d3bfce150213c800578ede7f4a760a0","tid":1692921,"uid":274732,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"以前一向討厭既人 食市 商戶全部都係藍<br />\n證明我眼光唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5e27b26a7ffa4ee9ced8aeb50268fdbd1f2231","tid":1692921,"uid":65091,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:28:31.000Z","msg":"一個人正氣真係有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a256540e36d6903f2a843c67dfb5cbd9dbe69204","tid":1692921,"uid":265485,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0d5e27b26a7ffa4ee9ced8aeb50268fdbd1f2231","tid":1692921,"uid":65091,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:28:31.000Z","msg":"一個人正氣真係有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:47:25.000Z","msg":"天佑人靚仔，不過個人比較on直d，過往發展一直冇又南咁好"},{"pid":"450d18dcd131dec128d1289bffefe8223e122d67","tid":1692921,"uid":10023,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:28:35.000Z","msg":"黃又藍"},{"pid":"49acd25f2ae695347359c2711c1a71885a08c8f6","tid":1692921,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T22:33:13.000Z","msg":"天佑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64fbaf2f6290bc7d5ccfc15d22792564dcf44b7","tid":1692921,"uid":137564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"ci